<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink368">
<l>erippū vilavat tūḻkaḻi paṉmalar</l>
<l>porippūm puṉkiṉ pukarniḻal varikkun</l>
<l>taṇpata vēṉi liṉpa nukarcci</l>
<l>yemmoṭu koṇmō perumaniṉ</l>
<l>ṉamme lōti yaḻivila ḷeṉiṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>O great one! Share with us the joy and delight </l>
<l>of the coolness in spring, </l>
<l>when many blooming flowers of Silk-cotton trees with flame-like blossoms,  </l>
<l>adorn the dappled shade of Puṉku trees,  </l>
<l>their flowers like puffed rice — </l>
<l>if only your tender, lovely-haired [girl] remains unharmed.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
